Class Version

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ibm.team.repository.common.Version
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<Version>

    public class Version
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<Version>
    Represents a simple version string like "3.0.1.5" or "4.0.3" with convenience methods for comparing versions.

        public int compareTo(Version v)
        Returns: 0 - This object is equals to the specified object. -1 - This object is less than the specified object. 1 - This object is greater than the specified object. Note that versions such as "1" and "1.0.0" are considered equal.
